Package: chaoticrage
Architecture: any
Depends: chaoticrage-data (= ${source:Version}),
	fonts-dejavu-core,
    ${shlibs:Depends},
    ${misc:Depends}
Description: Unusual 3D shooter game
 Unusual 3D shooter game with zombies, tanks, boats, and helicopters.
 Can be played in top-view, 3rd person or 1st person view.
 Has particle effects, decent physics, weather effects, and day-night effects.
 Multiple maps and gametypes.
 Fully moddable.
 .
 This is the main game code
 
Package: chaoticrage-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Unusual 3D shooter game - data files
 Unusual 3D shooter game with zombies, tanks, boats, and helicopters.
 Can be played in top-view, 3rd person or 1st person view.
 Has particle effects, decent physics, weather effects, and day-night effects.
 Multiple maps and gametypes.
 Fully moddable.
 .
 This is the data files and maps
